ill be some classics for athletes, like pasta, but the food will have a very French touch.\\\"\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French touch\", \"types\": [\"Q188451\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some classics\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"pasta\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes will also have access to \\\"grab and go\\\" food stands, including one dedicated exclusively to French cuisines cooked up by chefs.\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7472387468659376, \"rank\": 0.33826027749524734, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"chefs\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Renowned French chef Amadine Chaignot, who runs a restaurant and a caf\\u00e9-bistro in Paris, on Tuesday unveiled one of her recipes based on the iconic croissant.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2111, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7472387468659376, \"rank\": 0.33826027749524734, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_la